  "why_analysis": "The goal is to create an Odoo-focused context system that helps developers understand the project architecture quickly. Unlike generic memory systems, this leverages the indexer's parsed knowledge of Odoo structures. The user context section preserves the human decision-making and requirements that can't be automatically inferred from code - the 'why' behind architectural choices, user priorities, and session goals. This prevents context loss when resuming work or switching between agents."
